    public interface AttributeReadOptions<VALUE>
    This interface gives read access to the options attribute of an object.

    1.0.0
    Author:

      List<VALUE> getOptions()
      This method gets the options of this object.

    • Method Detail

      • getOptions

        List<VALUE> getOptions()
        This method gets the options of this object. The options are the available values to choose a selection from. The List shall not contain duplicate entries. It may contain the value null.
        Returns:
        the List with all available options.
